This allows preservation of the original client IP across the L4 proxy boundary.
⚠️ Important Clarification
Cilium is not required for PROXY Protocol.

PROXY Protocol is handled at L4 (Envoy → Traefik).
Cilium operates at L3/L4 (eBPF) and does not interfere unless explicitly configured.

