TLS is NOT terminated at Envoy
TLS is terminated inside the tenant cluster
Certificate Location

Certificates must exist in the tenant cluster, not at the edge.

Example: Rancher Deployment

For Rancher:

TLS certificate stored as Kubernetes Secret
